{"about_the_game":"Insipid is a puzzle game for vigilance.<br />\r\nThe game has a simple interface, where the player is presented with a field of cells of identical, at first glance, cells. The player must find and click on a cell that has a less saturated color than the rest. The higher the Player's score, the more implicit the difference between the cells becomes.<br />\r\nThe game has two modes: Normal and Time-Rush. In Normal mode, the player can look around the field and find the cells for as long as he likes, this mode is suitable for training vision. Time-Rush mode has a timer that is updated each time the player finds the correct cage. New records are recorded only in Time-Rush mode!","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1879570?t=1699094911","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1879570?t=1699094911","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879570/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1699094911","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879570/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1699094911","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Insipid is a puzzle game for vigilance.<br />\r\nThe game has a simple interface, where the player is presented with a field of cells of identical, at first glance, cells. The player must find and click on a cell that has a less saturated color than the rest. The higher the Player's score, the more implicit the difference between the cells becomes.<br />\r\nThe game has two modes: Normal and Time-Rush. In Normal mode, the player can look around the field and find the cells for as long as he likes, this mode is suitable for training vision. Time-Rush mode has a timer that is updated each time the player finds the correct cage. New records are recorded only in T